 m = \dfrac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}x_iy_i - n\bar{x}\bar{y}}{\sum_{i=1}^{n} x_i^2-n\bar{x}^{2}}\\ b= \bar{y} - m\bar{x} 
  \bar{x}: \text{mean of}\;\; x\\    \bar{y}: \text{mean of}\;\; y\\    x_i: \text{the $i^{th}$ number of}\;\;x\\    y_i: \text{the $i^{th}$ number of}\;\; y\\    n:\text{total numbers of}\;\; x \;\;\text{or}\;\; y 
